name: Wisdom Jobs
tag_list: jobs, careers, employment, job, career, job-portal
overview: Wisdom Jobs portal is a unique and specialized 4th generation job portal for job search and knowledge acquirement (a new feature).It is the integration of student activities (Planning, Preparation, Practice, Presentation and Personality) and job activities (searching, short listing, stabilizing, and satisfying). The outstanding features of Wisdomjobs.com, “Pragnya Meter” (a sophisticated talent filter which allows you to expose your technical and managing ability level along with the resume ) and “e- university” (a store-house of infinite skill set certifications, including 6000 skill set contents,50 million multiple option questions and 30 million interview questions) will facilitate the job seeker in achieving his goal.
